"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yis1665702679683.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yis1665702679683.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yis1665702679683\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Log off the SMTP server.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"yis1665702679683__topic_d134384e1_d134385e1_d134386e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yis1665702679683__p_d134387e1_d134388e1_d134389e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LogoffSMTP()</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yis1665702679683__section_jjw_bkh_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d613498e57\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yis1665702679683__section_tl3_dkh_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d613498e66\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"yis1665702679683__table_w4307ab1b5b5b3_w4308ab1b5b5_w4309ab1b5_w4310ab1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by SendMail in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yis1665702679683__table_w4307ab1b5b5b3_w4308ab1b5b5_w4309ab1b5_w4310ab1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yis1665702679683__table_w4307ab1b5b5b3_w4308ab1b5b5_w4309ab1b5_w4310ab1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yis1665702679683__table_w4307ab1b5b5b3_w4308ab1b5b5_w4309ab1b5_w4310ab1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yis1665702679683__table_w4307ab1b5b5b3_w4308ab1b5b5_w4309ab1b5_w4310ab1__entry__2\">Success</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yis1665702679683__table_w4307ab1b5b5b3_w4308ab1b5b5_w4309ab1b5_w4310ab1__entry__1\">-8</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yis1665702679683__table_w4307ab1b5b5b3_w4308ab1b5b5_w4309ab1b5_w4310ab1__entry__2\">Not logged on</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yis1665702679683__table_w4307ab1b5b5b3_w4308ab1b5b5_w4309ab1b5_w4310ab1__entry__1\">-9</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yis1665702679683__table_w4307ab1b5b5b3_w4308ab1b5b5_w4309ab1b5_w4310ab1__entry__2\">Network problems</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yis1665702679683__section_wxk_2kh_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d613498e129\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">LogoffSMTP</code> operation is used to log off the SMTP server, thus closing\n        the connection opened by <code class=\"ph codeph\">LogonSMTP</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Use <code class=\"ph codeph\">LogoffSMTP</code> only after all mails have been sent using\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">SendMail</code>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxt1665702677508.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>LogonSMTP</a><p>Log on to the designated SMTP server via TCP or TLS.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tnp1665702680599.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>SendMail</a><p>Send an email message, specifying the header, body, and attachments.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534114\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534114\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "LogoffSMTP Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Log off the SMTP server. LogoffSMTP() Parameters None Return Values Table 1. Values returned by SendMail in $status Value Description 0 Success -8 Not logged on -9 Network problems Description The LogoffSMTP operation is used to log off the SMTP server, thus closing the connection opened by LogonSMTP . Use LogoffSMTP only after all mails have been sent using SendMail . Related Links LogonSMTP Log on to the designated SMTP server via TCP or TLS. SendMail Send an email message, specifying the header, body, and attachments. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}